\c 16
\s Usuku lokubuyisana
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi emva kokufa kwamadodana amabili kaAroni ekusondeleni kwawo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, asesifa\x + 10.1,2.\x*.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Khuluma kuAroni umnewenu ukuthi angangeni langasiphi isikhathi e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele ngaphakathi kweveyili\x + Eks. 40.20,21. Eks. 30.10. Heb. 9.7,12,24,25; 10.19-22.\x*, phambi kwesihlalo somusa esiphezu komtshokotsho, ukuze angafi; ngoba ngizabonakala eyezini phezu kwesihlalo somusa\x + Eks. 25.22. 40.34,35. 1 Kho. 8.10,11,12.\x*.
\v 3 Elalokhu uAroni uzangena e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele: elejongosi ithole lenkomo, libe ngumnikelo wesono\x + 4.3.\x*, lenqama ibe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 1.10; 8.18.\x*.
\v 4 Uzakwembatha isigqoko esingcwele lelembu elicolekileyo\x + Eks. 28.39,42,43; 6.10; 8.7. Hez. 44.17,18.\x*, lokabhudula wangaphansi welembu elicolekileyo uzakuba senyameni yakhe, azibophe ngebhanti lelembu elicolekileyo, athandele ngeqhiye yelembu elicolekileyo; lezi yizembatho ezingcwele. Ngakho uzageza umzimba wakhe ngamanzi\x + Eks. 30.20; Levi 8.6.\x*, azembathe.
\v 5 Lakunhlangano yabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 4.14. Nani 29.11. 2 Lan. 29.21. Ezra 6.17. Hez. 45.22,23.\x* uzathatha izimpongo ezimbili zembuzi zibe ngumnikelo wesono, lenqama eyodwa ibe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa.
\v 6 Njalo uAroni uzanikela ijongosi lomnikelo wesono elingelakhe, azenzele inhlawulo yokuthula lokwendlu yakhe\x + 9.7; 15.11,17.24; Hez. 45.22; Heb. 7.27,28. 9.7.\x*.
\v 7 Athathe impongo ezimbili, azibeke phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* emnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 8 UAroni uzakwenza-ke inkatho phezu kwezimpongo ezimbili, enye inkatho ibe ngeyeN\nd kosi\nd* lenye inkatho ibe ngeyempongo yokususa.
\v 9 UAroni uzasondeza-ke impongo okuphezu kwayo inkatho yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ayenze ibe ngumnikelo wesono;
\v 10 kodwa impongo okuphezu kwayo inkatho yempongo yokususa uzayibeka iphilile phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ukwenza inhlawulo yokuthula ngayo, ukuyiyekela ihambe njengempongo yokususa enkangala.
\v 11 Njalo uAroni uzasondeza ijongosi lomnikelo wesono elingelakhe\x + 16.6.\x*, azenzele inhlawulo yokuthula leyendlu yakhe; ahlabe ijongosi lomnikelo wesono elingelakhe.
\v 12 Athathe umganu wokutshisela impepha ugcwele amalahle omlilo avele elathini phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 10.1. Nani 16.46. Isam. 8.3-5.\x*\nd*, lezandla zakhe zigcwele impepha elephunga elimnandi echolisisiweyo\x + Eks. 39.38.\x*, akulethe ngaphakathi kweveyili,
\v 13 abeke impepha phezu komlilo phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 30.1,7,8. Nani 16.7,18.\x*\nd*, ukuze iyezi lempepha lisibekele isihlalo somusa esiphezu kobufakazi\x + Eks. 25.21; Eks. 16.34.\x*, ukuze angafi.
\v 14 Athathe okwegazi lejongosi\x + 4.5. Heb. 9.13,25; 10.4.\x*, alifafaze ngomunwe wakhe phezu kwesihlalo somusa empumalanga\x + 4.6.\x*; langaphambi kwesihlalo somusa uzafafaza okwegazi kasikhombisa ngomunwe wakhe.
\p
\v 15 Abesehlaba impongo yomnikelo wesono engeyabantu\x + Heb. 2.17; 5.1; 9.7.\x*, alethe igazi layo ngaphakathi kweveyili\x + 16.2; Heb. 6.19; 9.3,7.\x*, enze ngegazi layo njengokwenza kwakhe ngegazi lejongosi, alifafaze phezu kwesihlalo somusa laphambi kwesihlalo somusa.
\v 16 Ngalokho uzakwenzela \add indawo\add* engcwele inhlawulo yokuthula\x + Eks. 29.36. Hez. 45.18. Heb. 9.22,23.\x*, ngenxa yokungcola kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, langenxa yeziphambeko zabo, ezonweni zabo zonke. Futhi uzalenzela njalo ithente lenhlangano, elihlala labo phakathi kokungcola kwabo.
\v 17 Kakungabi khona lamuntu ethenteni lenhlangano\x + Luka 1.10,21.\x*, ekungeneni kwakhe ukwenza inhlawulo yokuthula e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele aze aphume, esezenzele inhlawulo yokuthula, leyendlu yakhe, leyebandla lonke lakoIsrayeli.
\v 18 Uzaphumela-ke elathini eliphambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, alenzele inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 16.16. Eks. 30.6,10; 4.7,18.\x*, athathe okwegazi lejongosi lokwegazi lempongo, akufake empondweni zelathi inhlangothi zonke;
\v 19 afafaze okwegazi phezu kwalo kasikhombisa ngomunwe wakhe, alihlambulule, alingcwelise ekungcoleni kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 20 Lapho eseqedile ukwenzela \add indawo\add* engcwele ukubuyisana, lethente lenhlangano\x + 16.16,18; Hez. 43.20; 45.20.\x*, lelathi\x + 16.18.\x*, uzasondeza impongo ephilayo;
\v 21 uAroni abeke-ke izandla zakhe zombili enhlokweni yempongo ephilayo\x + Isa. 53.6.\x*, avume phezu kwayo bonke ububi babantwana bakoIsrayeli, leziphambeko zonke zabo, lezono zabo zonke, akubeke enhlokweni yempongo, a\add yi\add*yekele ihambe ngesandla sendoda efaneleyo, iye enkangala.
\v 22 Impongo izathwala-ke phezu kwayo bonke ububi babo, iye emmangweni owehlukanisiweyo\x + Isa. 53.11,12. Joha. 1.29. 1 Pet. 2.24.\x*; njalo izayiyekela impongo iye enkangala.
\p
\v 23 LoAroni uzangena ethenteni lenhlangano, akhulule izembatho zelembu elicolekileyo abezembethe ekungeneni kwakhe e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele\x + 6.11.\x*, azitshiye khona,
\v 24 ageze umzimba wakhe ngamanzi endaweni engcwele, agqoke izembatho zakhe, aphume, enze umnikelo wakhe wokutshiswa lomnikelo wokutshiswa wabantu, azenzele yena inhlawulo yokuthula leyabantu\x + 16.3,5.\x*.
\v 25 Lamahwahwa omnikelo wesono uzawatshisa elathini\x + 4.8-10.\x*.
\v 26 Lalowo oyekele impongo njengempongo yokususa uzahlamba izembatho zakhe, ageze umzimba wakhe ngamanzi\x + 16.28; 15.5.\x*, emva kwalokho angene enkambeni.
\v 27 Kodwa ijongosi lomnikelo wesono\x + 16.28. 15.5.\x* lempongo yomnikelo wesono, ogazi lazo langeniswa ukwenza inhlawulo yokuthula e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele, zizakhitshelwa ngaphandle kwenkamba; babesebetshisa izikhumba zazo lenyama yazo lomswane wazo ngomlilo.
\v 28 Lalowo okutshisayo uzahlamba izembatho zakhe, ageze umzimba wakhe ngamanzi, emva kwalokho angene enkambeni.
\p
\v 29 Kuzakuba yisimiso esaphakade kini: Ngenyanga yesikhombisa ngolwetshumi lwenyanga\x + Eks. 30.10. 23.27. Nani 29.7.\x* lizathobisa imiphefumulo yenu\x + 16.31; 23.32; Isa. 58.3.5. Dan. 10.12.\x*, lingasebenzi lamsebenzi, owokuzalwa elizweni lowemzini ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwenu.
\v 30 Ngoba ngalolusuku uzalenzela inhlawulo yokuthula ukulihlambulula; kuzo zonke izono zenu phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* lizahlanjululwa\x + Hlab. 51.2. Jer. 33.8. Heb. 10.1,2. 1 Joha. 1.7,9.\x*.
\v 31 Kulisabatha lokuphumula kini\x + 23.32.\x*; njalo lizathobisa imiphefumulo yenu; kuyisimiso saphakade.
\v 32 Njalo umpristi ogcotshiweyo\x + 4.3,5,16.\x*, owehlukaniselwe ukusebenza njengompristi esikhundleni sikayise\x + Eks. 29.29,30. Nani 20.28.\x*, uzakwenza inhlawulo yokuthula, agqoke izembatho zelembu elicolekileyo\x + 16.4.\x*, izembatho ezingcwele,
\v 33 enzele inhlawulo yokuthula indawo engcwele ngcwele\x + 16.16.\x*, lethente lenhlangano\x + 16.16.\x*, lelathi uzakwenzela inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 16.18.\x*, labapristi\x + 16.6.\x* labantu bonke bebandla\x + 16.24.\x* uzabenzela inhlawulo yokuthula.
\v 34 Lokhu kuzakuba yisimiso esilaphakade kini, ukwenzela inhlawulo yokuthula abantwana bakoIsrayeli kanye ngomnyaka\x + Eks. 30.10. Heb. 9.7,25.\x* ngazo zonke izono zabo. Wenza-ke njengokuba iN\nd kosi\nd* yalaya uMozisi.
